Amazing ultimate rares! These 2 classic Japanese cards are actually somewhat unique, they both have the word "REPLICA" in the bottom corner.

The reason they have the REPLICA tag is because these cards were originally printed as prize cards for the 1999 National Conferences! Only the original prizes have no text there.

All future OCG printings of those prize cards will carry the REPLICA tag - including Sengenjin, Zera the Mant, Serpent Night Dragon, Dark Magician Girl, Tri Horned Dragon, Firewing Pegasus, and a few others.
